very authentic taste, not for everybody taste
pros:
- very authentic local taste
- the pork satay taste is very good
cons:
- the restaurant is a bit dirty this is not some hip and fancy restaurant
- no rice
- the taste can be a bit too strong for some people
- the waiter talk very little english
- the food variety is very limited
- the price is not open. they dont really explain how much exactly for the food price
