christinecheng1
6115
Reviewed December 5, 2017
Super good banh xeo
If some one visited Da Nang and never come to this place for banh xeo is a great miss. Not easy to find because it is deep inside the ally. Along the way, several 'copy cat'. So make sure you go to the original shop. The menu is very simple and price is listed. We ordered 3 items and all are very good. The meat stick very tasty. The slice beef is perfectly prepared and cooked. Oh, most importantly, the meat sauce, it is very very good. It goes very well with the rice paper. The meat sauce, and the vegetables are free flow. The paper towel is chargeable. 2 of us total bill 185k dong.
