Fast and delicious
It was hard to find Ba Doung because it is located in an small alley.
I guess it is very famous for tourists and more than half of customers are koreans.
People don't need to order. They serve 'Banh xeo' and 'nem' autometically and fastly.
Also charge the money in proportion to the number of customer.
Worth a visit !!
