Hedgemeister-Global
Sydney, Australia
127103
Reviewed October 26, 2017
Tasty! Not for the mysophobic
Just don't look at the floor, the kitchen, the stainless steel tables and/or the recycling of food. Just eat, its sensational.
Love the fresh herbs and salad to combine with the pork sticks and pancake rice paper wraps. A cold beer over ice and everything tastes great.
Safer than Burger King at Chiang Mai airport.
