Best banh xeo in Da Nang!
Awesome banh xeo, nem lui and Bo la lot! Tasty as central dipping sauce - thumps up! Fast and efficient One of us is allergic to seafood they immediately whipped up banh xeo without prawns. Great friendly staff!
